        <div class="container mobile-container">
            <div class="spotlight-container mobile-spotlight-container">
                <div class="spotlight-content mobile-spotlight-content">
                    <h2 class="mobile-spotlight-title">AI-Powered Insights</h2>
                    <p class="mobile-spotlight-text">Our advanced algorithms analyze your spending patterns to provide actionable advice. Get notified when you're overspending and receive personalized tips to improve your financial health.</p>
